Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Evening’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Evening” game were:
6-9-1-1-9
(six, nine, one, one, nine)
